{"type":"data","nodes":[{"type":"data","data":[{"debug":1},true],"uses":{}},{"type":"data","data":[{"zotero":1,"inscriptions":6},{"title":2,"author":3,"date":4,"citation":5},"Un documento epigrafico inedito sulle terme di Agrigento",", , ","2023","\u003Cspan>Valentina Caminneci, Maria Concetta Parello, e Cristina Soraci, «Un documento epigrafico inedito sulle terme di Agrigento», in \u003Ci>Indagini archeologiche nell’insula IV del Quartiere Ellenistico Romano di Agrigento, 2014-2018\u003C/i>, a c. di Valentina Caminneci et al. (L’Aquila: One Group Edizioni, 2023), 537–49\u003C/span>",[7],{"file":8,"uri":8,"title":9,"status":10,"editionAuthor":12,"type":13,"objectType":17,"material":21,"condition":25,"layoutDesc":26,"handNote":33,"date":47,"places":52,"geo":61,"provenance":54,"provenanceGeo":65,"country":68,"region":69,"settlement":58,"repository":70,"idno":74,"textLang":76,"tmNumber":25,"facsimile":80,"letterHeights":86,"publications":87,"zotero":89,"keywords":91,"html":101,"bibl":102},"ISic001830","Building inscription of Martinianos",{"_":11},"draft",null,{"_":14,"ana":15,"ref":16},"building","#function.building","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/.html",{"_":18,"ana":19,"ref":20},"plaque","#object.plaque","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/259",{"_":22,"ana":23,"ref":24},"marble","#material.stone.marble","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/48.html","",{"layout":27},{"p":28,"rs":29,"damage":25},"Traces of three lines of ancient Greek are preserved, with guidelines above and below; upper, left and right margins are partially preserved. The text appears to maintain a consistent margin on the left, but not on the right.",{"_":30,"ana":31,"ref":32},"chiselled","#execution.chiselled","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1",{"lettering":34,"dimensions":35},"Tall, regular, narrow letters, v-cut, with small serifs on the termination of strokes. Small deep triangular interpuncts. Alpha has broken bar; epsilon tall, narrow, with equal short horizontals; theta and omicron are rhomboid; mu has vertical first and last, with the diagonals starting below the top and only desencing to the mid-point; nu is similar; rho has small curved, closed loop; sigma is lunate but rectilinear, with very short horizontals.",[36,43],{"type":37,"l":38,"from":39,"to":40,"h":41,"unit":42},"letterHeight","Line 1-2","line1","line2","110","mm",{"type":44,"l":45,"from":39,"to":40,"h":46,"unit":42},"interlinear","Interlineation line 1 to 2","20",{"_":48,"notBefore":49,"notAfter":50,"evidence":51},"Dated by reference to Flavius Martinianos, consularis of Sicily between 352 and 358 CE (Soraci)",352,358,"prosopography",[53,57],{"_":54,"type":55,"ref":56},"Agrigentum","ancient","http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462086",{"_":58,"type":59,"ref":60},"Agrigento","modern","http://sws.geonames.org/6541860",[62],[63,64],37.32084,13.58876,[66,67],37.297649,13.591579,"Italy","Sicily",{"_":71,"role":72,"ref":73},"Parco Archeologico Valle dei Templi","site","http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/200",{"type":75},"inventory",{"_":77,"mainLang":78,"languages":79},"Ancient Greek","grc",[77],{"n":81,"url":82,"height":83,"width":84,"desc":25,"surfaceType":85},"screen","ISic001830_tiled.tif","5520px","3680px","front",[],[88],", , , 2023, Un documento epigrafico inedito sulle terme di Agrigento",[90],"A7HRWIUH",[92,93,94,14,18,22,95,96,97,98,96,99,100,78],"isic001830","building inscription of martinianos",{"_":11},"agrigentum","agrigento","italy","sicily","parco archeologico valle dei templi","ancient greek","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φλάβιος Μαρτεινιανός\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φλάβιος\">Φ̣[λάβιος]\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"